name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: SummYT - Free YouTube Summary Generator for ChatGPT

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generate free YouTube Summaries with ChatGPT

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SummYT is a free Chrome Extension for summarizing videos on YouTube. Simply log into your ChatGPT account, find a video to summarize on YouTube, and our extension will do the rest.

Features that make SummYT unique:
- Beautiful and minimalistic reading experience
- Summaries are streamed instantly
- Completely free with no sign up! The only requirement is a free ChatGPT account
